        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "If the main thread is blocked by an invocation of "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsdocument/1515066-performactivitywithsynchronouswa"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " or "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsdocument/1515227-performsynchronousfileaccessusin"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", this method interrupts that blocking activity, performs the specified "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "block"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", and then resumes the blocking activity after "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "block"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " returns. Invocations of this method always return before the passed-in block is invoked."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "You can invoke this method when work is being done on a non-main thread and part of the work must be continued on the main thread. For example, "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsdocument/1515178-savetourl"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " uses this method when it has just completed the actual writing of the file during asynchronous saving and, to finish the saving operation, must invoke "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsdocument/1515083-updatechangecountwithtoken"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " and other methods on the main thread."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "This method can be invoked on any thread."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
